s covered.<br/><br/><img src="images/the_new_ron/8.jpg" alt="[image] " border="0"/><br/>First appearance of Le’ Goop.<br/><br/><img src="images/the_new_ron/9.jpg" alt="[image] " border="0"/><br/>Francois indicates that only a pea sized amount of Le’ Goop is used.  The tagline for Le’ Goop is “The secret is in the sea urchin.”<br/><br/><img src="images/the_new_ron/10.jpg" alt="[image] " border="0"/><br/>Kim is happy with the results.<br/><br/><img src="images/the_new_ron/11.jpg" alt="[image] " border="0"/><br/>Rufus is pleasantly surprised.<br/><br/><img src="images/the_new_ron/12.jpg" alt="[image] " border="0"/><br/>Ron screams after seeing what his hair looks like.<br/><br/>
